Defendant Matthew A Demmer appears via videoconferencing from the Jefferson County Jail, in custody, along with Public Defender Jeffrey De La Rosa (the PD appears for bond-purposes only; Mr. Demmer does not qualify for PD representation).  Public Service Special Prosecutor Melanie Flint appears for the State of Wisconsin.

Mr. Demmer indicates that his address is 2607 Wesley Avenue, Janesville 53545.
Service of the Complaints admitted, reading waived, the charges and maximum penalties are recited.
As to case #22CM23 only the Court finds probable cause to exist in the Criminal Complaint.

[The Court adjourns the Initial Appearance in each case.]

--no possession or ingestion of controlled substances without a valid prescription
--no possession of drug paraphernalia
